According to multiple sources, Popular Evangelist, Reinhard Bonnke is dead. Reinhard Bonnke was a German Pentecostal evangelist, principally known for his gospel missions throughout Africa. Bonnke has been an evangelist and missionary in Africa since 1967. Bonnke has overseen 75 million recorded conversions to Christ He had several crusades and outreach in several parts of the world including Nigeria during his lifetime. 